quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,Alif Laam Miim
  32,2,(Qur’an) ni igitabo kidashidikanywaho cyahishuwe giturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose
  32,3,"Cyangwa bavuga ko (Muhamadi) ari we wayihimbye? (Siko bimeze), ahubwo yo ni ukuri kwaturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe ngo uyifashishe mu kuburira abantu batagezweho n’umuburizi uwo ari we wese mbere yawe, kugira ngo bayoboke"
  32,4,"Allah ni we waremye ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo mu minsi itandatu, hanyuma aganza ku ntebe y’icyubahiro (Ar’shi). Nta wundi murinzi cyangwa umuvugizi muzagira utari we. Ese ubwo ntimutekereza"
  32,5,"Ayoborera mu kirere gahunda zose (z’ibiremwa) zigana ku isi, maze zikazamuka zigana iwe mu munsi umwe ungana n’imyaka igihumbi mu yo mubara (ku isi)"
  32,6,"Uwo (Allah) ni Umumenyi w’ibyihishe n’ibigaragara, Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  32,7,"We watunganyije buri kintu yaremye, akanarema umuntu mu ibumba utari uriho"
  32,8,Hanyuma agira amazi asuzuguritse (intanga) inkomoko y’ukororoka kwe
  32,9,"Maze aramutunganya, amuhuhamo roho imuturutseho; abaha ukumva, amaso n’imitima. Ariko ni gake mushimira"
  32,10,"Baranavuga bati \"Ese (nidupfa) tukaburira mu gitaka, tuzasubizwa ubuzima bundi bushya?\"Ahubwo bo bahakana kuzahura na Nyagasani wabo"
  32,11,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Malayika w’urupfu ubashinzwe azabatwara ubuzima; hanyuma kwa Nyagasani wanyu ni ho muzasubizwa"